LKB installation guide 

1. download and install Xcode (Xcode_9.2.xip) https://developer.apple.com/xcode/
2. download and install Command Line Tools (Command_Line_Tools_macOS_10.13_for_Xcode_9.2.dmg) https://idmsa.apple.com/IDMSWebAuth/login?appIdKey=891bd3417a7776362562d2197f89480a8547b108fd934911bcbea0110d07f757&path=%2Faccount%2F&rv=1
3. download and install XQuartz (XQuartz-2.7.11.dmg) https://www.xquartz.org/
4. download and install MacPorts (MacPorts-2.4.2-10.13-HighSierra.pkg) https://www.macports.org/
5. Terminal: install libtool			sudo port install libtool
6. Terminal: install libusb +universal			sudo port install libusb +universal
7. download and uncompress OpenNI SDK v1.5.7.10 (OpenNI-Bin-Dev-MacOSX-v1.5.7.10.tar.bz2) http://openni.ru/openni-sdk/openni-sdk-history-2/index.html
8. Terminal: navigate to OpenNi folder			cd ///OpenNI-Bin-Dev-MacOSX-v1.5.7.10
9. Terminal: install OpenNi			sudo ./install.sh
10. Terminal: prevent error			sudo ln -s /usr/local/bin/niReg /usr/bin/niReg
11. download and uncompress SensorKinect (SensorKinect-unstable.zip) https://github.com/avin2/SensorKinect
12. double-click to uncompress  SensorKinect/Bin/SensorKinect-unstable/Bin//SensorKinect093-Bin-MacOSX-v5.1.2.1.tar.bz2
13. Terminal: navigate to Sensor-Bin-MacOSX-v5.1.2.1 folder		cd ///Sensor-Bin-MacOSX-v5.1.2.1
14. Terminal: install SensorKinect			sudo ./install.sh
15. download and uncompress NiTE v1.5.2.23 (NITE-Bin-MacOSX-v1.5.2.21.tar.bz2) http://openni.ru/openni-sdk/openni-sdk-history-2/index.html
16. Terminal: navigate to NITE-Bin-Dev-MacOSX-v1.5.2.21		cd ///NITE-Bin-Dev-MacOSX-v1.5.2.21
17. Terminal: install NITE			sudo ./install.sh
done
